      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FARMOR AGAIN (1) scored two back then was always well back and could manage only a 22 length 8th at Rockhampton (24.97). Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. Can discover winning form. TIGER BAILEY (8) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Missed the frame latest (22.66) when seventh over 380m at this track in a OPEN. Looks well placed here and among the chances. EMMY PANAMA (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when third (22.27) at this track. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Overdue and gets her chance. APPLICATION (7) missed when well in commission last time but can improve.",
